      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"move on\" sounds so simple when you say it, but it's not. Every single thing I built is dust. My wife thinks I'm a hero, my parents are so proud of the \"success\" i had. if i go back now, i'm just the guy who blew it all. i see the numbers and the emails and it's just a constant weight. it feels like this shame is just... permanent. like it's who i am now. how do you even \"start again\" when you've lost your dignity?",
